\par \hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0 JEAN BUTLER: Then we can go tell Dr. Kent what you did today.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0 GENIE: Doctor.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0 JEAN BUTLER: Dr. Kent, \hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0 uh-huh.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0 STACY KEACH: Genie said the word "doctor."
