\par }{\insrsid8853670\charrsid2827064 \hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0 DAVID RIGLER: I remember making the commitment, in my mind, for a three-month period, which obviously got extended much longer.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0 INTERVIEWER: Ho\hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0 w long was she\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 did she stay?
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0 DAVID RIGLER: She was with us approximately four years.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0 STACY KEACH: Genie's new home was in a neighborhood near Children's Hospital. She lived here with David Rigler, his wife Marilyn, and the Rigler children.
\par }{\insrsid11485374\charrsid2827064 \hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0 6 How long did G\hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0 enie live with the Rigler\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s?
