\par \hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0 GENIE: Potty chair.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0 MARILYN RIGLER: You slept in the potty chair?
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0 GENIE: Mmm-hmm. Potty chair.
