erving science, he was no longer serving his career, he abandoned him, he let him go. Itard gave up. He asked Madame Geurin, the housekeeper, to take the boy in, down the street from the deaf school, and there they lived a rather gray, sad, forlorn existe
\hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0 n\hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0 ce, the two of them.\hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0  }{\insrsid8799195\charrsid2827064 
